test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [-6, -6, -6, -6, -6, -6] == []
  Left contains 6 more items, first extra item: -6
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-6, -6, -6, -6, -6, -6]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0] == []
  Left contains 6 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [-60, -60, -60, -60, -60, -60] == []
  Left contains 6 more items, first extra item: -60
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-60, -60, -60, -60, -60, -60]
